Priority: Normal
Severity: Minor
Reproducibility: Always
Platform: Google Chrome 63.0.3239.132
OS: Windows
OS Version: 7 x86

Summary: The mouse cursor is not changed from default to pointer in the drop-down main menu after
hovering the mouse over its elements

Description: The mouse cursor is not changed from default to pointer in the drop-down main menu after
hovering the mouse over its elements

Steps To Reproduce:

1. Go to the site http://prestashop*******
2. Open the drop-down main menu
3. Hover the mouse over the main menu elements
4. Pay attention to the mouse cursor

Actual result: The mouse cursor is not changed from default to pointer in the drop-down main menu after
hovering the mouse over its elements

Expected result: The mouse cursor is changed from default to pointer in the drop-down main menu after
hovering the mouse over its elements

Additional Information:

Environment:
Mozilla Firefox 52.4.0
IE 11.0
Chrome 63.0.3239.132

